What are the features of the Obstacle Cross Drive Simulator?

Obstacle Cross Drive Simulator is a classic racing simulator game with 3d roads and features a variety of obstacles and ways to cross them, challenging your driving skills and reaction time. Drive your vehicle on different tracks and terrains, trying to overcome high walls, cliffs, water hazards, and obstacles. The game features high-quality 3D graphics for a more realistic experience. There are four different modes of play: traffic mode, free mode, city mode, and parking mode, which test your familiarity with traffic signals, the pursuit of speed, obstacle avoidance skills, and parking proficiency. Earn points in-game to unlock items and new car skins in the garage waiting for you and have an even more enjoyable experience.

What's special about the gameplay of Obstacle Cross Drive Simulator?

The gameplay of Obstacle Cross Drive Simulator is very simple, use the WASD or arrow keys on your keyboard to control the steering wheel, throttle, and brakes of your truck, or click the on-screen buttons to operate. Drive through a realistic 3D city road, avoiding various obstacles, and arrive at your destination as fast as possible. The game has multiple challenging levels, and each level requires you to try to overcome a series of driving challenges.

Play Obstacle Cross Drive Simulator and enjoy a fun, and addicting online truck driving simulator game.

If you're a gaming enthusiast who loves obstacle races and truck driving, then Obstacle Cross Drive Simulator is a must-play game for you. Play four different modes, each of which provides challenges and enjoyment, allowing you to understand basic acceleration and improve your driving skills, reaction time, and speed. Start your driving journey now and enjoy the acceleration of the truck!
